metadata.name: BNA - Rise Token
metadata.description:
The Black NFT Art - Rise Collection is a limited edition 500/500 collection of NFTs that give access to The Rise Collector Club, a private collector club with exclusive perks.

The Rise Collector Club aims to build a thriving community of collectors who buy from and support Black artists, onboard new Black collectors into NFTs, and support the career growth of Black NFT artists. Allies are welcome to buy BNA Rise tokens and join the club! To learn more about the BNA Rise Token and how to join the Club, visit our website at www.blacknftart.co
